705093f-a.title: Brooklyn: Jamaica Avenue - Euclid Avenue
705093f-a.text:
790-820 Jamaica i Ve., south side, from Euclid Ave., to Crescent Street,
showing in the background, a B.M.T. Elevated line. The building in front
of which is a truck, was once Harman's Casino Grove. In 1873 it was Dist-
1er's Hotel and Brewery.
April 1923.
Eugene L Armbruster Collection.
